channel.title: INDIR3CT (Heniel) Notify [Dubstep/ Hybrid trap]
channel.description:
Heyo! Super excited to share this track with you, it’s something I’ve never done before. Been listening to a lot of amazing Auxy dubstep artists such as @Cornea, @anon2811266, and @Xiejra, and thought I’d give it a shot. (A lot different than my normal future bassey type stuff lol) I uploaded the track to my Alt account, which I also wanted to share with you guys.
https://soundcloud.com/heniel/notify Here is the track, any feedback would be amazing! P.s. I’ll be posting a lot more on my alt soon.
